    "description": "<strong>《浮生千百事》是一款成熟的3D视觉小说游戏，讲述了有关姐妹情谊，母女情，因他人离世而悲痛不已，以及带着伤口继续活下去的故事。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687960/extras/8c4ebacfc76291b6bb4b5427969fbb58.poster.avif?t=1762953793\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687960/extras/8c4ebacfc76291b6bb4b5427969fbb58.webm?t=1762953793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687960/extras/8c4ebacfc76291b6bb4b5427969fbb58.mp4?t=1762953793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>朱侬的人生在36岁时分崩离析，她的职业生涯遇到瓶颈，开始对人生失去热情，私生活也变得一团糟。原本就已经糟糕的状况继续急转直下，因为她接到消息后赶到医院，发现与自己关系疏远的母亲已经病危。这一天对于朱侬的人生来说是最重大的日子，如果她没有做出任何改变，那么这天就可能是她人生中最后一天。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687960/extras/0ada8a19ad8ab9947dfdc3550795befd.webp?t=1762953793\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br><strong>重温过去</strong><br>探索朱侬的回忆，拼凑出她的过去，包括那个隐藏在深处的悲伤秘密。<br><br><strong>改变现在</strong><br>借助你对朱侬内心创伤的了解，改变她在这一天的人生轨迹，解锁新的对话选项并修复破碎的人际关系。<br><br><strong>拥抱未来</strong><br>如果人生已经跌到最低谷，那么接下来一定会柳暗花明。协助朱侬找到心灵的平静，并在人生最悲惨的日子里发现生活周遭的幽默、美丽与希望。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687960/extras/7402a83cbfbbde5ba36ec93672df4ea3.poster.avif?t=1762953793\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687960/extras/7402a83cbfbbde5ba36ec93672df4ea3.webm?t=1762953793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687960/extras/7402a83cbfbbde5ba36ec93672df4ea3.mp4?t=1762953793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《浮生千百事》支持全英文配音<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687960/extras/0ada8a19ad8ab9947dfdc3550795befd.webp?t=1762953793\" width=600 height=40 /></span>",
